quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  94,1,HAVE WE not lifted up your heart
  94,2,and relieved you¹ of the burden
  94,3,which weighed down your back
  94,4,And have We not given you high renown
  94,5,With every hardship there comes ease
  94,6,With every hardship there comes ease
  94,7,When your prayers are ended resume your toil
  94,8,and seek your Lord with all fervour